"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9305398426073402, \"rank\": 0.07404755501828568, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999692890928, \"rank\": 3.0710882916731515e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP  PublishedMay 30, 2024, 04:19 AM  UpdatedMay 30, 2024, 04:40 AM  LOS ANGELES - Former Olympic all-around gymnastics champion Gabby Douglas on May 29 abandoned her bid to make an unlikely comeback at this year's Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Line-of-sight_propagation\", \"score\": 0.6258675009662505, \"rank\": 0.5977822757310021, \"text\": \"LOS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Line-of-sight_propagation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Line-of-sight_propagation\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabby Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas, 28, returned to the sport in 2024 after an eight-year break, with the goal of making the US team for Paris.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.7915335487015013, \"rank\": 0.26151744239561514, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9305398426073402, \"rank\": 0.07404755501828568, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999692890928, \"rank\": 3.0710882916731515e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the three-time Olympic gold medallist told ESPN she had now scrapped her comeback after suffering an ankle injury in training.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999625393650068, \"rank\": 3.744536361735053e-05, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love this sport and I love pushing my limits,\\\" Douglas told ESPN.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.7915335487015013, \"rank\": 0.26151744239561514, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999625393650068, \"rank\": 3.744536361735053e-05, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope I can inspire both my peers and the next generation of gymnasts that age is just a number, and you can accomplish anything you work hard for.\\\"\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas made history by becoming the first Black gymnast to win the Olympic all-around gold medal at the 2012 London games.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.7915335487015013, \"rank\": 0.26151744239561514, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.99999994267114, \"rank\": 5.667315371640633e-08, \"text\": \"2012 London games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was also a part of the US squads which won gold medals in the team events at the 2012 and 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9305398426073402, \"rank\": 0.07404755501828568, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas told ESPN she has not given up hope of returning to Olympic gymnastics, revealing she will now target qualification for the 2028 Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.7915335487015013, \"rank\": 0.26151744239561514, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999625393650068, \"rank\": 3.744536361735053e-05, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I proved to myself and to the sport that my skills remain at an elite level,\\\" Douglas said.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"score\": 0.7915335487015013, \"rank\": 0.26151744239561514, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_O._Douglas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My plan is to continue to train for the LA 2028 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"ran